Class GNSConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.main.GNSConfig

  • public class GNSConfig
extends Object
    Author:
    arun, westy Contains config parameters for the nameservers and logging functionality. This file should be used for server-only properties. Client properties are GNSClientConfig.
